data.description: Investor Special! Spacious 3-bedroom Ranch Style Home on full basement, 4 Sides Brick, featuring an open floorplan of a large lot, and a full basement. The home features a large front yard and a large backyard. Cash or Conventional financing is recommended. Excellent location, 4 minutes from shopping and dining. This home is in "good" condition, 4 sides Brick with "strong bones". The home features an open floor plan, a large kitchen, a spacious master bedroom, and a fenced backyard. The large backyard is excellent for dogs, children, and entertaining friends. Excellent location close to interstate I-20, I-285, and I-75. Only 16 minutes to Atlanta airport. Come view this Home today!
